For Thanksgiving, I was asked to bring pumpkin pie. So, I brought one (store bought - for shame) pie & then I made this cheesecake. WHAT A HIT! Even my parents were impressed. :) Here's a cheesecake tip: to avoid the butter dripping, put the springform pan on a cookie sheet. Problem is, the butter will continue to leak, even after you remove it from the oven. I sat mine on paper towels all the time, except when it was being served. A doily would work, too.

