This cheesecake is fantastic!! It's gotten rave reviews from my friends and is requested so much that I make it several times each fall. The first few times I made the recipe, I had varying results with the topping...one time the cream cheese mixture was too thin and the caramel drizzled on top actually "sank" and disappeared...another time I overcompensated, making the topping too thick and it wouldn't swirl with the caramel. The best balance seems to be adding 3 1/2 to 4 Tbsp. of the whipping cream to the mixture, rather than the 5 T. called for in the recipe.

